<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.7.11">
<l>ñālamuṟṟu muṇṭā lilaittuyil nārāya ṇaṉukkivaḷ</l>
<l>mālatā kimakiḻn taṉaḷeṉṟu tāyurai ceytataṉai</l>
<l>kōlamār poḻilcūḻputu vaiyarkōṉ viṭṭucit taṉcoṉṉa</l>
<l>mālaipat tumval lavarkaṭkil laiva rutuyarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who master the garland of ten [verses] composed by Viṭṭucittaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">king of the people of Putuvai, surrounded by beautiful groves</l>
<l>about the words spoken by a mother,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying, “Having gone mad for Nārāyaṇa who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having consumed the entire earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">sleeps on a banyan leaf, she rejoices”,</l>
<l>there will be no suffering.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
